Package richtest.Parser.AST

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnnotationPropertiesVisitor
    This is a visitor that when its applied to a node , it indicated whether the node has annotations or not And if it has annotations it returns the annotations
    ASTCodeBlockVisitor
    This is a visitor that when applied to a node (ideally a CompilationUnit) , it filters out different types of nodes And categorizes them into Noneblocks and blocks Noneblocks are blocks that dont have a block comment and will be defined as blocks Blocks are the blocks that will be compared to themselves in database and if they are not the same it will count as a change
    ASTCommentStrip
    A visitor that strips all the comments from the node when its applied to that node
    ASTTestBlockVisitor
    Visitor for test block nodes
